body.description: Armor All Car Wipes Multi-Pack includes a variety of car wipes that clean your vehicle’s interior surfaces and exterior glass surfaces to provide a “just-detailed” look. Start with Armor All Cleaning Wipes to lift away dirt and debris and reveal your car’s rich, natural beauty without harming delicate automotive surfaces. These multi-surface car cleaning wipes are effective on vehicle dashboards, vinyl, fabric, carpet, consoles, leather and more. Additionally, cleaning wipes won’t dry out, damage or fade automotive surfaces. Follow up with Armor All Original Protectant Wipes to help preserve your vehicle’s rich look by protecting the interior from harmful elements like UV rays and oxidation. These protectant wipes also function as a preventive measure against cracking, fading, discoloration and premature aging. Both the protectant wipes and cleaning wipes are lint-free and will not leave a greasy residue on your hands. End with Armor All Glass Wipes, which leave a crystal clear, streak-free shine on your car’s glass surfaces by easily removing filmy residue, road grime, bugs, fingerprints and more. All these car cleaning wipes provide effective cleaning in convenient, disposable wipes. Help keep your vehicle looking and feeling like new with Armor All.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars DON’T THINK JUST BUY!!!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. When I tell you I bought this just to see if it would work and really clean my car as good as the product says I put it to the test. I own a car that has been sitting for just over 3 yeasts collecting dust,dirt,sand(idk how😂) and literally everything that you can think of. I was doubtful it would work. I first started off with cleaning my windows and it came out crystal clear (I suggest you use only one for your windows if you can. The wipe is usually soaked in cleaner so you can reuse it). I was impressed. I then took out ONE literally ONE wipe and started going ham. I cleaned my entire door with one wipe. I noticed the wipe goes dry after a little but that’s no problem. Even when the wipes dry it still collects all the dirt and grime. I then use the same dirty rag to clean some parts of my exterior and it worked. Don’t even get me started on the polisher it worked wonderfully. Thanks for reading the review and just to let you know. I stopped half way through cleaning to write this review. I will forever buy this product to clean my car and my cars in the future. So with this all being said DON’T THINK JUST BUY!!

reviews.reviewText: Armour All has always been a popular brand. Product arrived fast. Make sure when u go to use the protecting that you thoroughly wipe and leave the dash where it looks damp. If not this gets really streaky looking. The glass cleaner was amazing. Removes vape film great from vehicle windows. Will buy again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars All good except the glass cleaner(which is really bad).
reviews.reviewText: The cleaner and protection wipes are 100% perfect. They work exactly as advertised and I'm completely happy with them. HOWEVER, and this is a big however... The glass wipes are completely useless. There is something in the wipes that makes me have to wipe again every 2-3 days. I thought at first that my inside windshield was just a little dirty and that's why the wipes didn't work so well. But I've almost used every single wipe in the canister at this point, and every time I use the wipes it seems fine. Then after a couple of days I start to see streaks again and have to reapply. I switched and just bought Windex and a roll of paper towels(total of $5 for about 6 months worth of Windex). I wet the paper towel with Windex and wipe the window and it's weeks before I have to redo it.I'm very disappointed, but I think they are putting something in the glass cleaner so that you need to use it very frequently. I'm still giving it a 4* review because the other two products are top-notch at cleaning and protecting your car's interior. It's impressive how well the protecting wipes work.

Reviewed in the United States on June 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Tubs Seal Well, Some Products Work Better Than Others
reviews.reviewText: Overall, I like the product, the tubs seal well, so no need to worry about drying out. My favorite of the three was the cleaning wipes as they were very very effective. My least favorite was the glass wipes, I had to use 5-7 wipes just to make sure my window wasn't left with streaks, The window wipes didn't feel very damp and made for a tough cleaning job. The protectant wipes were good, they did the job but did leave a bit of a streaky look at times, (its possible that its user error but I've tried many different application techniques).
